@startuml
title TestForge - Ciclo de Vida da FailureSignature na Curadoria em 3 Camadas

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}

[*] --> DETECTED : execution_failed / capture_failure_context

state DETECTED
state NORMALIZED
state CLASSIFIED
state EVIDENCE_PACKAGED
state CATALOG_CHECKED
state AGENT_SELECTED_L2
state PATCH_PROPOSED
state PATCH_VALIDATING
state PATCH_REJECTED
state PATCH_APPLIED_TEMPORARILY
state REEXECUTING
state PASSED_STEP
state PROGRESSED
state STAGNATED
state REGRESSED
state ERROR_CHANGED
state UNRESOLVED
state CONFIDENCE_GATE
state HEALING_RETRY
state GENERAL_LLM_L3
state RESOLVED
state ABANDONED

DETECTED --> NORMALIZED : normalize_failure / build_failure_signature_json
NORMALIZED --> CLASSIFIED : classify_failure / assign_family_and_taxonomy_case
CLASSIFIED --> EVIDENCE_PACKAGED : package_evidence / reuse_recording_and_run_artifacts
EVIDENCE_PACKAGED --> CATALOG_CHECKED : evidence_ready / query_healing_catalog_by_family_and_symptom

state CATALOG_CHECKED {
  [*] --> CATALOG_MATCH_FOUND : match_exact
  [*] --> CATALOG_NO_MATCH : no_entry_found
  --
  state CATALOG_MATCH_FOUND
  state CATALOG_NO_MATCH
}

CATALOG_MATCH_FOUND --> PATCH_PROPOSED : apply_primary_strategy / use_catalog_entry_fix
CATALOG_NO_MATCH --> AGENT_SELECTED_L2 : no_catalog_entry / route_to_specialist_agent

AGENT_SELECTED_L2 --> PATCH_PROPOSED : agent_selected / heal() determínistico primeiro
AGENT_SELECTED_L2 --> PATCH_PROPOSED : regras_exauridas / _llm_fallback() via _build_prompt()

PATCH_PROPOSED --> PATCH_VALIDATING : patch_created / validate_patch

PATCH_VALIDATING --> PATCH_REJECTED : patch_invalid / persist_rejection_reason
PATCH_VALIDATING --> PATCH_APPLIED_TEMPORARILY : patch_valid / apply_to_temporary_version

PATCH_REJECTED --> AGENT_SELECTED_L2 : alternative_specialist_agent_available / retry_with_different_approach
PATCH_REJECTED --> GENERAL_LLM_L3 : no_valid_specialist_patch / escalate_to_general_llm
PATCH_REJECTED --> UNRESOLVED : all_layers_exhausted / mark_unresolved

PATCH_APPLIED_TEMPORARILY --> REEXECUTING : temporary_version_ready / rerun_step

REEXECUTING --> PASSED_STEP : step_passed / compare_with_previous_failure
REEXECUTING --> PROGRESSED : execution_advanced / create_progress_checkpoint
REEXECUTING --> STAGNATED : no_progress / keep_failure_signature_active
REEXECUTING --> REGRESSED : regression_detected / trigger_rollback
REEXECUTING --> ERROR_CHANGED : error_signature_changed / require_reclassification
REEXECUTING --> UNRESOLVED : no_solution_found / check_remaining_layers

PASSED_STEP --> RESOLVED : layer_1_match / update_catalog_hit_counter
PASSED_STEP --> RESOLVED : layer_2_or_3_learned / register_new_entry_in_catalog

PROGRESSED --> AGENT_SELECTED_L2 : remaining_failure_exists / select_next_agent_or_strategy
PROGRESSED --> GENERAL_LLM_L3 : specialist_agents_exhausted / escalate
PROGRESSED --> RESOLVED : flow_completed / accept_patch_chain

STAGNATED --> AGENT_SELECTED_L2 : alternative_specialist_available / try_next_agent
STAGNATED --> GENERAL_LLM_L3 : specialist_agents_exhausted / escalate
STAGNATED --> UNRESOLVED : all_layers_exhausted / mark_unresolved

REGRESSED --> ROLLED_BACK : rollback_required / restore_last_stable_version
ROLLED_BACK --> AGENT_SELECTED_L2 : rollback_completed / select_safer_specialist_strategy
ROLLED_BACK --> GENERAL_LLM_L3 : no_safe_specialist_strategy / escalate
ROLLED_BACK --> UNRESOLVED : all_layers_exhausted / mark_unresolved

ERROR_CHANGED --> CLASSIFIED : reclassify_required / rebuild_failure_signature

GENERAL_LLM_L3 --> CONFIDENCE_GATE : llm_suggested_candidate / check confidence

CONFIDENCE_GATE --> PATCH_PROPOSED : confidence >= 0.5 / accept_proposal
CONFIDENCE_GATE --> UNRESOLVED : confidence < 0.5 / low_confidence_reject
CONFIDENCE_GATE --> UNRESOLVED : taxonomy_invalid / invalid_proposal

REEXECUTING --> HEALING_RETRY : l3_retry_needed / retry_with_new_error

HEALING_RETRY --> PATCH_PROPOSED : depth < MAX_RETRY_DEPTH(1) / _run_healing_cycle_again
HEALING_RETRY --> UNRESOLVED : depth_exceeded / mark_unresolved

GENERAL_LLM_L3 --> ABANDONED : llm_limit_exceeded / preserve_unresolved_report

UNRESOLVED --> AGENT_SELECTED_L2 : layer_2_still_available / retry_with_different_agent
UNRESOLVED --> GENERAL_LLM_L3 : only_layer_3_remaining / controlled_llm_fallback
UNRESOLVED --> ABANDONED : no_more_layers / close_failure_as_unresolved

RESOLVED --> [*] : resolved_and_registered
ABANDONED --> [*] : unresolved_history_preserved

DETECTED --> ABANDONED : unrecoverable_missing_evidence
NORMALIZED --> ABANDONED : normalization_impossible
CLASSIFIED --> ABANDONED : classification_blocked_by_invalid_signature
EVIDENCE_PACKAGED --> ABANDONED : evidence_package_insufficient
AGENT_SELECTED_L2 --> ABANDONED : no_agent_available
PATCH_APPLIED_TEMPORARILY --> ROLLED_BACK : temporary_version_corrupted / rollback
REEXECUTING --> ABANDONED : unrecoverable_execution_infrastructure_error

note right of CATALOG_CHECKED
  Layer 1 — Catálogo de Cura:
  Consulta healing-catalog.jsonl por
  match exato de família + sintoma.

  Custo: ZERO de LLM.
  Latência: <50ms.
  Cobertura esperada: ~70% dos casos.
end note

note right of AGENT_SELECTED_L2
  Layer 2 — Agente Especialista:
  Roteia pelo FAMILY_AGENT_MAP:
  FAM-01→Selector, FAM-02/05→Timing,
  FAM-03→Context, FAM-04→State,
  FAM-06/07→Input.

  FAM-08/09/10/11 → sem agente → L3 direto.

  Cada agente heal(): regras determínisticas
  primeiro. Ao final, _llm_fallback() via
  _build_prompt() se não resolveu.

  Prompt otimizado (~200 tokens).
  Custo LLM baixo.
  Cobertura esperada: ~20%.
end note

note right of GENERAL_LLM_L3
  Layer 3 — _run_healing_cycle():
  LLMHealer real (Azure OpenAI) ou
  MockLLMHealer (fallback simulado).

  - load_llm_config() em CuradorAutomatico.__init__()
  - AZURE_OPENAI_KEY + AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT → LLMHealer
  - Env vars ausentes → MockLLMHealer
  - Model configurável: AZURE_OPENAI_MODEL (default gpt-4.1-mini)
  - FAMILY_PROMPTS selecionados por family=""
  - Prompt enxuto (~500 tok)

  Confidence gate: >= 0.5 aceita proposta.
  < 0.5 → UNRESOLVED.

  Retry depth: MAX_RETRY_DEPTH=1.
  ERROR_CHANGED → 1 retry com novo erro.
  REGRESSED/STAGNATED → rollback.
  PASSED → _register_learned() no catálogo.
end note

note right of CONFIDENCE_GATE
  LLMHealingProposal.confidence >= 0.5:
  - strategy in ALLOWED_STRATEGIES
  - family in FAMILIES
  - taxonomy_id in TAXONOMIES[family]

  Se qualquer validação falha,
  confidence é zerada → rejeitado.
end note

note right of HEALING_RETRY
  ERROR_CHANGED:
  O erro mudou após o patch.
  _run_healing_cycle() é chamado
  novamente com depth+1.

  MAX_RETRY_DEPTH = 1 (CuradorAutomatico).
  Se depth >= 1 após retry → UNRESOLVED.
end note

note right of REGRESSED
  REGRESSED significa que o patch piorou o fluxo,
  quebrou steps previamente válidos ou removeu
  comportamento necessário.

  Rollback obrigatório antes de qualquer
  nova tentativa em qualquer layer.
end note

note right of ERROR_CHANGED
  ERROR_CHANGED significa que a assinatura
  da falha mudou após uma tentativa.

  A falha deve voltar para CLASSIFIED
  para reclassificação antes de prosseguir.
end note

note right of RESOLVED
  RESOLVED exige:
  - patch aceito e validado por execução
  - catálogo atualizado (contador ou nova entrada)
  - classificação taxonômica preservada no relatório
  - camada usada (1, 2 ou 3) registrada
end note

@enduml
